Class GuildVoiceUpdateEvent

    GuildVoiceLeaveEvent, GuildVoiceMoveEvent

    public class GuildVoiceUpdateEvent
extends GenericGuildVoiceEvent
    GuildVoiceUpdateEvent
    Generic event that combines GuildVoiceLeaveEvent and GuildVoiceMoveEvent for convenience.
    Fires when a Member that was previously connected to a VoiceChannel leaves the previously connected Channel.

    Use: See when a Member leaves a channel
